            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Committed them to prison; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " this to be sure the Jews had yet retained power from the Romans to do. All this is but as a foil, to illustrate more the riches of God’s mercy towards Saul. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
