        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "As for Saul, he made havoc of the church,.... Did evil to the saints, destroyed them that called upon the name of Christ, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 9:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and persecuted and wasted the church of God, as he himself says, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Galatians 1:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and now did Benjamin, of which tribe Saul was, ravine as a wolf, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 49:27",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Entering into every house; where the saints dwelt: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and haling men and women: in a violent manner, without any regard to age or sex: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "committed them to prison; delivered them up into the hands of the chief priests and magistrates, in order to be committed and sent to prison; this he himself confesses, Acts 22:4. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
